value.name: NNPP to Nigerians: Reject ‘it is my turn’ politics, support Kwankwaso ...
value.snippet: The New Nigeria Peoples Party (NNPP) has asked Nigerians to support Rabiu Kwankwaso, its presidential candidate, to “rescue” the country.
